[
    {
        "source_sentence": "大乘遍照光明藏無字法門經",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874a09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大唐天竺三藏地婆訶羅再譯",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874a11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是我聞：一時，佛住王舍城耆闍崛山，與大",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874a12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩及比丘僧無量百千億那由他眾俱。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874a13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其諸菩薩，一切皆得大智善權，悉能通達無字法藏，具樂說辯不違真俗，勇猛精進永離蓋纏，調伏諸根無所執著，憐愍眾生如視一子，愛重實智如大寶洲，慚愧為身定慧為首，以大慈悲而為體性，知善不善、實不實法，照了二空住勝妙地，得大名稱永安隱眠，決定修行最上之法，永離胎藏下劣之身，示現受生守護國土，諸所施為普遍賢善，離於三界能救三界，其行清淨善達自他，皆得具足如是功德。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874a23_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其名曰：",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874a23_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "勝思惟菩薩，勝趣行菩薩，妙音菩薩，美音菩薩，辯具菩薩，辯聚菩薩，珠髻菩薩，千輻菩薩，法輞菩薩，法響菩薩，蓮花面菩薩，蓮華眼菩薩，持地菩薩，持世菩薩，聲遍大地菩薩。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874a27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是等菩薩摩訶薩，一切皆是童子像類，於此眾中而為上首，各各與己眷屬等俱。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874a29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，觀世音菩薩，與無量無數灌頂受職諸菩薩眾之所圍繞；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "得大勢菩薩，與無量億大梵天眾之所圍繞；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "勝思惟菩薩，與無量菩薩及天主帝釋之所圍繞；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "虛空藏菩薩，與無量四天王眾之所圍繞；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "眾所知識菩薩，與無量婇女之所圍繞；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "普賢菩薩、離疑菩薩、不空見菩薩、止諸蓋菩薩、無量善巧藥王菩薩、藥上菩薩等，各與無量菩薩大眾之所圍繞；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b08_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "長老舍利弗、摩訶目乾連、摩訶迦葉等，各與一切大阿羅漢之所圍繞；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至十方恒河沙等一切世界所有日月諸天子等，各以威光來至佛所，以佛神力，彼彼威光不能照曜，猶如聚墨比閻浮金；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又有無量那羅延天，及以水天德叉迦龍王、阿那婆達多龍王等，亦與眷屬之所圍繞；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "美音乾闥婆王，亦與無量乾闥婆眾之所圍繞；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無濁迦婁羅王，與七億迦婁羅王眷屬圍繞；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至十方恒沙世界一切菩薩，各請己佛，與眷屬俱，來至此間娑婆世界，持諸上妙出世供具，供養於佛及菩薩已，各禮佛足却住一面，坐蓮華座瞻仰世尊。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時勝思惟菩薩摩訶薩即從座起，偏袒右肩，右膝著地，合掌向佛，而作是言：",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b22_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我為四眾，欲問如來二字之義，惟願如來為我解說，令我等輩咸得利益。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時世尊告勝思惟菩薩言：",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b25_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b25_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來豈為一眾生故出現於世？",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃為利益無量眾生出現於世。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b27_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今乃能為四眾故，請問於我二字之義。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隨汝所問，當為汝說。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b28_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於是勝思惟菩薩蒙佛聽許，白佛言：",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874b29_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有何等法，菩薩摩訶薩應當除滅及以守護？",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有何法，如來克證及以覺知？",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是二義惟願為說。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，佛讚勝思惟言：",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉，善哉！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c04_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c04_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝已成就無量福慧，復為如來加威神力，乃能問我如是之義。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諦聽，諦聽！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c06_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善思念之！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c06_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吾當為汝分別解說。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c07_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有一種法，菩薩摩訶薩應當除滅。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等一法？",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂欲貪。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是一法，菩薩摩訶薩應當除滅。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有一法，菩薩摩訶薩應當除滅。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等一法？",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c11_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂瞋恚。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c11_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是一法，菩薩摩訶薩應當除滅。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c12_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
