    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有一法，菩薩摩訶薩應當除滅。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等一法？",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c15_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂我執。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是一法，菩薩摩訶薩應當除滅。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c16_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c17_2",
