        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等一法？",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c24_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂疑惑。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是一法，菩薩摩訶薩應當除滅。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c25_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有一法，菩薩摩訶薩應當除滅。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c26_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等一法？",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂無明。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c27_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是一法，菩薩摩訶薩應當除滅。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c28_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如上所說如是等法，菩薩摩訶薩應當除滅。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0874c29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝問於我，復有何法，菩薩摩訶薩應守護者，今為汝說。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有一種法，菩薩摩訶薩常當守護。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等一法？",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂己所不欲，勿勸他人。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是一法，菩薩摩訶薩常應守護。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩守護此法，即是守護諸佛如來一切戒藏。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a05_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如諸菩薩，自愛命者則不應殺，自愛財者則不應盜，自愛妻者不應侵他，自愛實語不應誑彼，自愛和合不應間他，自愛正直不應邪綺，自愛柔軟不應惡罵，自愛止足終不於他而生貪欲，自愛仁恕終不於他而生瞋恚，自愛正見終不教他令生邪見。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a11_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a11_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是菩薩發意說言，『我今敬順如來正教，應當勤心守護此法』，是名菩薩摩訶薩守護一法。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a13_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我見如是諸菩薩等，欲求無上大菩提者，悉為樂故而求菩提，無有為苦求之者也。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a15_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故我說己所不欲，勿勸他人。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是等法，菩薩摩訶薩應當守護。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a17_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時勝思惟菩薩復白佛言：",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a18_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等之法，如來克證及以覺知？",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a19_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "惟願為我開演其義。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a19_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無有一法而是如來所覺所證。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a20_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於諸法中無覺無證，此是如來所證所覺。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切諸法本無有法，如來覺證；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a22_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切諸法本無有滅，如來覺證；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切諸法性離二邊，如來覺證；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切諸法本無有實，如來覺證。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a26_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切諸法，皆從自業因緣力故而得生起；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而是因緣，念念不住猶如電光，如是業緣，如來覺證。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875a28_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故我說以因緣故而諸法生，以因緣故而諸法滅，若離因緣，則無業報。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是等事，如來覺知。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b01_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是所覺一切法性，是名遍照光明之藏。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何故法性名之為藏？",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以諸眾生世出世智，皆依此藏而得生故。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如以實智觀彼法性，智依彼生，故名為藏。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我亦復說一切諸法如幻如焰，如水中月，如是等事，如來覺證；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b07_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b07_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸法性相，一味解脫，如是等事，如來覺證。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是解脫一味法性，是名遍照光明之藏。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又有一法如來覺證。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等一法？",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b11_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂諸法不生不滅、不增不減、不來不去、不取不捨、非因非緣。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b13_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是等法，如來覺證。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b13_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來了知一切諸法無有自性，不可為喻，無有文字之所辯說。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是之法，如來覺證。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如上所說如是之法，悉是如來所覺所證。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」當佛說此遍照光明藏無字法時，有微塵數諸菩薩等得住十地；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又有無量諸菩薩等住於諸地；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b19_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又有無量諸菩薩等證得百千諸大三昧；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b20_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又有無量塵數眾生發阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b21_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又有無量無邊眾生得阿羅漢果；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又有無量無邊眾生得脫地獄、餓鬼、畜生種種諸苦，生人天中受勝妙樂；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b23_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸在會眾悉不唐捐，無有一人而空過者。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時佛告羅睺羅言：",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我此法要，汝當受持。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時彼會中有九十億菩薩摩訶薩聞是語已，承佛神力，白佛言：",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b27_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b27_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我等誓於娑婆世界後時後分，見有堪能為法器者，我當為彼宣說是經，惟願世尊不以為慮。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875b29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時四天王復白佛言：",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c01_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若當來世有善男子及善女人，能有受持此經典者，我當擁護，諸有願求皆令滿足。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c03_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此善男子及善女人，能持此經，是法器故。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時世尊，見九十億諸菩薩等，及四天王如是請已，便作是言：",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我此所說遍照光明藏無字法門，我得佛來未曾演說，今為汝等而演說之。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼未來世諸眾生等，若得聞此希有法門，當知是人久已成就無量福慧；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人則為承事供養於我；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c10_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人則為荷擔佛大菩提；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c11_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人決定當得成就辯才；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人決定當得清淨佛土；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c12_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人臨命終時定當得見阿彌陀佛，菩薩大眾之所圍繞；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人常見我身在靈鷲山，及見此等諸菩薩眾；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c15_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人則為已得無盡法藏；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人得宿命智；",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人不墮惡道。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次善男子！",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今我說是未曾有法，若當來世有善男子及善女人，設有已作五逆等罪，聞此法門，若能書、持、讀誦、解說，或勸他人書、持、讀誦及以解說，我見是人不墮惡道，其人所有諸煩惱障、業障、報障，皆得清淨，其人來世具得五眼，其人則為一切諸佛所共灌頂，其人則為諸佛世尊及諸菩薩之所護念，其人來世在在所生，具足諸根無有缺減。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c25_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛說是經已，勝思惟菩薩摩訶薩等，及諸比丘，天龍八部，聞佛所說，皆大歡喜，信受奉行。",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c27_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大乘遍照光明藏無字法門經",
        "from": "T17n0830_001:0875c28_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]